net.classic.update

Check for Updates demo.
Very basic class for checking updates of a ROM or Application.

TODO: Clean up UI and add new features.

Instructions:

Requires Java 1.6 or above. Built using OpenJDK 7.

Option A. 
Import project into Eclipse. 
Requires Android SDK 14 and above. 
Requires Android ADT 20.0.3 and Android SDK Tools r20.0.3.
Debug and export as needed.

Option B (recommended):
In terminal, execute:
    android update project --target android-15 --path /PATH/TO/PROJECT
    # for use with debugging
    ant debug install 
    # for use with release
    ant release install

Have fun!
